          <td colspan="2" valign="top" class="titulo2">Foreign in our own country<a href="#_edn1" name="_ednref1" title=""><sup>1</sup></a> <span class="texto2">by <a href="../../issue9/filippakopoulou/bio.php" class="link3">Maria Filippakopoulou</a></span></td>
